# SmartSSD

The postgres code for VLDB 2022 submission, "Deploying Computational Storage for HTAP DBMSs Takes More Than Just Computation Offloading".

## Point of Interest

Lookup for code sections wrapped up with the definitions listed below.


| Flag | Content |
| ------ | ------ |
| SMARTSSD | Code related to SmartSSD operations for PostgreSQL. (e.g., integration between postgres and SmartSSD) |
| SMARTSSD_DBUF | **D**irty **BUF**fer (DBUF) maintenance and flush logic |
| VERSION_INDEX | Version index related logic |
